channel.title: (317) small development, Godwars Dungeon for non-Pi or Delta
channel.description:
So the base I started developing had all the NPC's for GWD already on it but it didn't have a dungeon so i decided to make one. So far I've spent 5 hours and 25 minutes coding it. I know what I've done isn't very good but like I said, it's a small development and may encourage coders to start making a fully working Godwars for non-PI or Delta CC is appreciated but please don't flame
Progress video: [URL=http://s1094.photobucket.com/albums/i455/nsf_/?action=view&current=2011_06_18_19_41_15_764x496.mp4][IMG]http://i1094.photobucket.com/albums/i455/nsf_/th_2011_06_18_19_41_15_764x496.jpg[/img][/URL]
